{"type":"question","id":16843,"title":"武汉红十字会把民间捐的口罩拿去卖，拦截民间物资，大量物资放在地上根本没人管，大家怎么看？","uid":28448,"topics":[276,163,5262],"contents":"民间自发组织的捐赠口罩，包括校友会捐赠的口罩很大一部分都是写明了给武汉协和医院的，定点捐赠。<br>\n却被红十字会毫不讲理的拦截，拿来分配给权贵阶层和倒卖赚钱，还没来得及处理的大量的口罩物资就随意放在地上，万一下雨全部玩完。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/view/status/l/public/4b6737218457f8e.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/view/status/l/public/4b6737218457f8e.jpg\" alt=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/view/status/l/public/4b6737218457f8e.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n邮政小哥拍下的视频，一边拍一边说给大家看一下，这些全是口罩，这还只是冰山一角。（←小哥原话）【看上去真的不缺口罩，缺的是良心】<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/view/status/l/public/4097e9656433885.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/view/status/l/public/4097e9656433885.jpg\" alt=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/view/status/l/public/4097e9656433885.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/view/status/l/public/4e8db467e4a67ea.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/view/status/l/public/4e8db467e4a67ea.jpg\" alt=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/view/status/l/public/4e8db467e4a67ea.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/view/status/l/public/bc307f5fa6319f8.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/view/status/l/public/bc307f5fa6319f8.jpg\" alt=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/view/status/l/public/bc307f5fa6319f8.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/view/status/l/public/fa4494bf1ac7dfb.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/view/status/l/public/fa4494bf1ac7dfb.jpg\" alt=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/view/status/l/public/fa4494bf1ac7dfb.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n现在全世界的口罩都断货，实际上这些口罩都到达了武汉，就被这样处理着。<br>\n而武汉最好的医院却天天缺物资，像个乞丐一样的要在网上乞讨，像奴隶一样的请求红十字会给他们分配口罩。<br>\n<br>\nhttps://www.douban.com/group/topic/164171375/ 这个帖子里的视频被删了，是说工作人民不小心收漏嘴，证明民间捐赠的口罩被卖了。<br>\n文字版如下：<br>\n有没有医用口罩？<br>\n冇得货（没有货）<br>\n怎么你们都没有那不是见了鬼了？<br>\n我们可以买<br>\n我知道你们想买，（但是）前两天我们才卖了十万出去<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n我的图片怎么不显示","date":"2020-01-31","agreeCount":5,"discussionCount":3}